trans-unit.source: Exception occurs when the Metadata Editor tries to convert a sparse column to categorical.
trans-unit.target: Exception occurs when the Metadata Editor tries to convert a sparse column to categorical.

trans-unit.source: This exception occurs when the <link xlink:href="370b6676-c11c-486f-bf73-35349f842a66" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Metadata Editor</link> tries to convert a sparse column to categorical.
trans-unit.target: This exception occurs when the <link xlink:href="370b6676-c11c-486f-bf73-35349f842a66" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Metadata Editor</link> tries to convert a sparse column to categorical.

trans-unit.source: You will receive this error when trying to convert sparse columns to categorical with the <ui>Make categorical</ui> option.
trans-unit.target: You will receive this error when trying to convert sparse columns to categorical with the <ui>Make categorical</ui> option.

trans-unit.source: Azure machine Learning does not support sparse categorical arrays, so the module will fail.
trans-unit.target: Azure machine Learning does not support sparse categorical arrays, so the module will fail.

trans-unit.source: Make the column dense by using <link xlink:href="72bf58e0-fc87-4bb1-9704-f1805003b975" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">convert to dataset</link> first or do not convert the column to categorical.
trans-unit.target: Make the column dense by using <link xlink:href="72bf58e0-fc87-4bb1-9704-f1805003b975" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">convert to dataset</link> first or do not convert the column to categorical.

trans-unit.source: Sparse columns cannot be converted to Categorical.
trans-unit.target: Sparse columns cannot be converted to Categorical.
